{"tid":2309091,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[犯國安法?]巴士公司對國產電巴非常不滿","createTime":"2020-12-02T10:02:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T11:39:16.000Z","uid":101945,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"da3afefc4fe88ad81f07ff10da61645d5e27f8fa","tid":2309091,"uid":101945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T10:02:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2817483/%E3%80%90e%EF%BC%8B%E8%BB%8A%E8%B7%AF%E4%BA%8B%E3%80%91%E6%84%89%E6%99%AF%E7%81%A3%E9%9B%BB%E5%8B%95%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E8%A9%A6%E9%A9%97%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E5%87%BA%E7%88%90%20%20%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%B0%8D%E5%9C%8B%E7%94%A2%E9%9B%BB%E5%B7%B4%E9%9D%9E%E5%B8%B8%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2817483%2F%25E3%2580%2590e%25EF%25BC%258B%25E8%25BB%258A%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E4%25BA%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%2584%2589%25E6%2599%25AF%25E7%2581%25A3%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%258B%2595%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E9%25A9%2597%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%2588%2590%2520%2520%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E5%25B0%258D%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2594%25A2%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E9%259D%259E%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF&d=u42ujRIT%2FE%2FeodHrCKN%2BObY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=8113b618\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2817483/%E3%80%90e%EF%BC%8B%E8%BB%8A%E8%B7%AF%E4%BA%8B%E3%80%91%E6%84%89%E6%99%AF%E7%81%A3%E9%9B%BB%E5%8B%95%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E8%A9%A6%E9%A9%97%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E5%87%BA%E7%88%90%20%20%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%B0%8D%E5%9C%8B%E7%94%A2%E9%9B%BB%E5%B7%B4%E9%9D%9E%E5%B8%B8%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF</a><br />\n<br />\n早前，環保署提供綠色運輸試驗基金，資助運輸公司研究轉用電動車的可能性，當中愉景灣客運對兩部華夏神龍沂星電動巴士的詳測報告，近日正式公布，結果為非常不滿意。<br />\n<br />\n    愉景灣客運對兩部華夏神龍沂星電動巴士非常不滿意<br />\n    出車率只有 40% 及 58%<br />\n    乘客對電動巴士表示支持<br />\n<br />\n報告列舉出夏神龍沂星電動巴士的幾大「罪狀」，主要是電池、空調系統及空氣壓縮機表現不穩定，導致經常要進行維修，更指電池退化程度在第 2 年大增，難以執行正常營運，在第 3 年更甚，導致兩部車在測試期內的出車率只有 40% 及 58%。值得注意的是，測試車的里程只有約 23,000 公里，一般公共巴士此里程仍屬「新車」狀態。<br />\n<br />\n當然，報告中亦有列出電日巴士的好處，包括乘客認為車廂寧靜，而車長亦覺得操作問題不大。此外，在營運行駛成本方面，電動巴士每公里較對照組的柴油車少 $4.77，低足 74%，亦可減低 50% 二氧化碳排放 (連同充電設施計算)。"},{"pid":"006d7966a4b63ea5ae0f179d5b7b888206f570a7","tid":2309091,"uid":68598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T10:02:54.000Z","msg":"講咩支那唔好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n擺明太好你地唔識用"},{"pid":"b1f03b02cc407b83cd0295471c13b8896ff96fa0","tid":2309091,"uid":245441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T10:04:23.000Z","msg":"美股電車三寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aa649cf2b15892d83d7bcdd64e3d08294d1c69f","tid":2309091,"uid":57513,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T10:05:06.000Z","msg":"駛唔駁焗買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a22197acdf1d23fc45b9576c5059a69d56fc94ab","tid":2309091,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T10:07:03.000Z","msg":"冇可能! 係用家問題<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea655352e8d66288e961993307821e588ca0cd60","tid":2309091,"uid":290869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T10:07:54.000Z","msg":"營運成本大減，但維修成本大增"},{"pid":"ae9671b4ea5610b61e1f49b6c310936945f9c81b","tid":2309091,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T10:10:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b32aadeb577456ddbe86ec6db6d73250a9b0654","tid":2309091,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T10:24:01.000Z","msg":"買係好平 但支那劣質製品成日要維修<br />\n維修費仲貴過買多部其他國家出產"},{"pid":"8c9e51cab17ed9f9bccea69884672150b209fbe1","tid":2309091,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b32aadeb577456ddbe86ec6db6d73250a9b0654","tid":2309091,"uid":201604,"like":1,"disli